<text top="2166" left="141" width="331" height="50" font="font4" id="p1_t42" reading_order_no="41" segment_no="14" tag_type="text">view  of  the  system.</text>
<text top="2213" left="194" width="623" height="51" font="font1" id="p1_t43" reading_order_no="42" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">But  not  all  software  systems  are</text>
