<text top="2309" left="143" width="675" height="53" font="font3" id="p1_t45" reading_order_no="44" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">example  is  the  control  system  for  ad-</text>
<text top="2358" left="142" width="674" height="51" font="font1" id="p1_t46" reading_order_no="45" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">vanced  aircraft.  The  control  system  is</text>
<text top="2406" left="144" width="673" height="51" font="font1" id="p1_t47" reading_order_no="46" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">implemented  as  a  distributed  system</text>
<text top="2454" left="144" width="674" height="51" font="font1" id="p1_t48" reading_order_no="47" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">across  many  processors  throughout</text>
<text top="2501" left="143" width="673" height="51" font="font1" id="p1_t49" reading_order_no="48" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">the  structure  where  they  can  be  close</text>
<text top="2548" left="143" width="675" height="53" font="font3" id="p1_t50" reading_order_no="49" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">to  sensors  and  control  surfaces.  An-</text>
<text top="2596" left="143" width="673" height="53" font="font3" id="p1_t51" reading_order_no="50" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">other  example  is  software  in  any  large</text>
<text top="2644" left="144" width="673" height="53" font="font3" id="p1_t52" reading_order_no="51" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">system  that  must  constantly  adapt  in</text>
<text top="2694" left="143" width="673" height="51" font="font1" id="p1_t53" reading_order_no="52" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">a  rapidly  changing  environment.  In</text>
<text top="2741" left="143" width="673" height="53" font="font3" id="p1_t54" reading_order_no="53" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">these  cases  the  characteristics  of  the</text>
<text top="2792" left="144" width="674" height="49" font="font6" id="p1_t55" reading_order_no="54" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">hardware,  the  interconnections,  and</text>
<text top="2838" left="143" width="673" height="53" font="font3" id="p1_t56" reading_order_no="55" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">the  environment  continually  influence</text>
<text top="2886" left="144" width="674" height="51" font="font1" id="p1_t57" reading_order_no="56" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">the  software  design.  The  software  en-</text>
<text top="2933" left="142" width="675" height="53" font="font3" id="p1_t58" reading_order_no="57" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">gineer  must  either  know  the  system</text>
