<text top="547" left="871" width="604" height="80" font="font13" id="p1_t67" reading_order_no="65" segment_no="2" tag_type="text">as  well  as  software.</text>
<text top="868" left="870" width="669" height="50" font="font4" id="p1_t68" reading_order_no="66" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">a  system  engineer  to  the  team  will  be</text>
